   4C:  Call  BattleCamTargetActor  ( .Actor:Enemy0 )
   5C:  Call  MoveBattleCamOver (  20` )
   6C:  Call  8024ECF8  ( FFFFFFFF 00000001 00000000 )
   84:  Call  SetAnimation      ( .Actor:Enemy0 00000001 003B0503 )
   9C:  Call  SetActorSpeed     ( .Actor:Enemy0 *Fixed[6.0] )
   B0:  Call  SetGoalToTarget   ( .Actor:Enemy0 )
